{"type":"message","id":"5845600d","parentId":"5a20347e","timestamp":"2026-03-20T23:16:44.031Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-21 07:16 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防/智慧城市\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n要求：\n- 搜索最新资讯、政策、市场动态\n- 整理3-5条关键信息\n- 每条信息包含：标题、来源、核心内容摘要\n\n搜索完成后，将结果整理输出。"}],"timestamp":1774048604028}}
